(1, 'Warren Pope', 8961879941, 'warrenpope2010@gmail.com', 7, 1, 'Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.', '2020-04-18'),
(2, 'Manish', 8989547688, 'manish@example.com', 5, 4, 'It\'s a very good college\r\nFaculty is pretty good. Teachers interacts with students.\r\nCollege management  needs to improve.\r\nInfrastructure is good.', '2020-04-22'),
(3, 'Amit', 7869094532, 'amit@example.com', 8, 4, 'This Institute needs to improve it\'s infrastructure. Faculty is good. Placements needs to be improved. Institute should focus on proper improvement of their students. ', '2020-04-22'),
(4, 'Shraddha Chhabra', 8852850991, 'shraddhachhabra@example.com', 6, 4, 'This University has many courses and it\'s good to have different courses at a same place. It\'s Infrastructure is also good. Faculty needs to be improved. Price for each courses is high. Overall development for students is good.\r\n', '2020-04-22'),
(5, 'Manish Malhotra', 6205992740, 'manishmalhotra@example.com', 9, 5, 'University is too good. Infrastructure is awesome. Faculty is good. Courses needs to improve their syllabus. University should focus on personality development. They should have courses for improvement of personality.\r\nPlacements related things should be discussed with students.', '2020-04-22'),
(6, 'Umar ', 9088564739, 'umar@example.com', 10, 2, 'This medical college is good. Infrastructure needs to improve. Faculty should improve. Training should focus on every aspects. So that all the students becomes well trained.', '2020-04-22'),
(7, 'P K Maiti', 9980349154, 'maiti@example.com', 11, 1, 'The place is very bad,AC is not working. Stuff are not properly trained..... The number this people have given is always switched off.Excellent infrastructure and placement.Not good academy and wastage of money,  no industrial training\r\nAll reviews are fake, they said, job will provide, 100% placements all this was not a job, no job guaranty and employees have got a change.', '2020-04-22'),
(8, 'Animesh', 8921850932, 'animesh@example.com', 12, 5, 'Best Dental Collage & Hospital in Kolkata.\r\nTreatment is free, Good doctors, & treatment, clean, run by Govt of West Bengal.Infrastructure is amazing. Good for all class people. Stuffs are good. Cleanliness is ok. They give best treatment. Many dentist passed out from this institution every year. One thing that is bad of this institution is they take long time for treatment.', '2020-04-22'),
(9, 'Anwar', 9832175903, 'anwar@example.com', 13, 4, 'Nice Infrastructure. I dont know about placements and all. I have visited FDDI, Kolkata. Clean and nice environment. A good college for FOOTWEAR STUDENTS, others streams are good too...\r\n\r\nBut the dump factors includes ENVIRONMENT - there are lot of factory and a big sewage line beside it, making it harder to breathe , just so smelly...', '2020-04-22'),
(10, 'Kamaljeet', 8743992038, 'kamaljeet@example.com', 9, 5, 'Best University with good number of placements. Always encourages to try and explore new things. Best place to choice your career. Faculty always encourages students to try new things,specially  always encourage students    for Entrepreneurship.Good infrastructure, Peaceful environment,No Ragging Campus in India.', '2020-04-22'),
(11, 'Divya', 9932567694, 'divya@example.com', 9, 1, 'Worst University. They mentioned that they have the tfw quota but i called and came to know there is no such quota.', '2020-04-22'),
(12, 'Soumil Das', 8898205284, 'soumil@example.com', 9, 4, 'The hospitality of the staff at Brainware University is commendable. Very well-behaved, professional people to work with.Very good campus, much under rated may be due to its location, but a perfect place to study and make career at an affordable cost too.', '2020-04-22'),
(13, 'Goldy ', 6205985432, 'goldy@example.com', 9, 2, 'Be aware to all students, \r\nThey aren\'t home University, \r\nit\'s affiliated with Moulana Abul Kalam University. \r\nBut the didn\'t inform me prior to admit . Even though it\'s not mentioned in the article', '2020-04-22'),
(14, 'Rajna', 8897949834, 'rajna@example.com', 9, 1, 'They took 5k from by Brother for seat booking and ehen he went to them to allot a seat then he came to know that his seat was already booked. They returned only 2k after that . Totally injustice and shameless behavior from the account department.', '2020-04-22'),
(15, 'Pureman', 6205889844, 'pureman@example.com', 9, 3, 'Unlike many other Universities, I haven\'t heard of a single incident of ragging from Brainware University. This campus is safe, secure, well-facilitated and well-reputed.\r\nLike', '2020-04-22'),
(16, 'Md Faruk', 7766548732, 'faruk@example.com', 9, 3, 'Not a great University..\r\n.but as per value....it\'s great....and campus is overall good. The eco friendly campus is more attractive for student,very nice place...and much more facilities', '2020-04-22'),
(17, 'Payel Das', 9898653892, 'payel@example.com', 9, 4, 'The quality of education imparted at Brainware University, is par excellence.This is great place for higher education.This place is best for students as the campus is very eco friendly and teachers are also very friendly to the students', '2020-04-22'),
(18, 'Dhimani  ', 6205998765, 'dhimani@example.com', 9, 5, 'Excellent infrastructure. Well mentioned green campus with residential facilities for boyos and girls. Professors are very helpful. Affordable course fees. Updated well researched syllabi. Excellent labs and workshops with a good number of equipment. Canteen and food court. Excellent campus life and so on...', '2020-04-22'),
(19, 'Indranil', 6205887693, 'indranil@example.com', 9, 2, 'The worst University. The behavior of the VC is so rude, he don\'t even know how to behave! He is asking his employees to work  like a slave! He is a filthy, rude, illiterate, mannerless, boastful person. I am afraid about the future of the students of this useless money making university.', '2020-04-22'),
(20, 'Moumita', 8984822231, 'moumita@example.com', 9, 4, 'This is the best university in Kolkata.....Nice infrastructure and eco friendly ragging free campus.Affordable course fees and quality education', '2020-04-22'),
(21, 'Debobratah', 8798098789, 'debobratah@example.com', 9, 4, 'rainware University is the brainchild of Mr. Phalguni Mookhopadhayay’s prolonged effort and is recognized as one of the top private universities in West Bengal. Built on a lush and expansive 9-acre campus at Kazipara Barasat, the university is at a stone’s throw from the nearest bus stop at Chaapadali. It is an autonomous body offering specialized courses in BTech, MTech, BSc, MSc, BCom, MCom, BBA, MBA, BCA, MCA, BPharm, DPharm, BA, MA, PhD, as well as Diploma courses in an array of subjects. The university also provides a student-centralized service in terms of accommodation, social space, and other relevant facilities. The university houses more than 90 faculty members. Our esteemed teaching faculty comprises of renowned research scholars and academician of the leading institutes from within and across West Bengal. Ever since its inception in 2016, the University boasts a 100-percent student pass rate, till date.\r\n\r\nWe provide a state-of-the-art infrastructure in modern teaching equipments, laboratory facilities that includes multimedia lab, electronics lab, computer lab, pharmaceutical lab, a well-stocked central library, tutorial, career development centre, counselling and a host of other opportunities to render a wholesome learning experience to our students. At Brainware University we believe in delivering quality education through interactive learning and extra-curricular activities, as we continually strive for a moral and academic enrichment in creating future scholars and professionals.', '2020-04-22'),
(22, 'Warren Pope', 8961879941, 'warrenpope2010@gmail.com', 9, 2, 'It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using \'Content here, content here\', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for \'lorem ipsum\' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by accident, sometimes on purpose (injected humour and the like).', '2020-04-25');
